                <h2 class="govuk-heading-l">1. Introduction</h2>
                <p class="govuk-body">
                    This glossary provides information on acronyms and terminology used within the Get information about pupils (GIAP) website.
                    The glossary is not intended to act as an instructional text on how to use the system.
                    Information on how to use the system is provided via this <a class="govuk-link" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BBG3HYigspw&amp;feature=youtu.be" id="help--user-guide--link" target="_blank">video</a>.
                </p>
